SUMMARY:BWA: Professional Bike Health Checks
DESCRIPTION:Professional bike health checks available for BWA families as part of Earth Week 2026.\n\nThe PTA and APL are hosting a professional bike health check service. Drop off bikes between 8:00 AM and 9:00 AM in front of the school. Collection is at the end of the school day. Advance booking is required via the school events portal. Pricing: 10 GBP for small bikes, 14 GBP for big bikes (24 inches and above).
CATEGORIES:COMMUNITY
