DESCRIPTION:Parents are invited to visit classrooms to share languages other than French or English during French Week.\n\nAs part of the 6th edition of 'Mai des Langues', parents who speak a language other than French or English at home are invited to come into class to introduce their language through a story, nursery rhyme, or everyday objects. This session takes place during the French Week from 08 June to 12 June.
