SUMMARY:BWA Y1b: 1B Trip to Natural History Museum
DESCRIPTION:1B class trip to the Natural History Museum to explore the Dinosaur Exhibitions.\n\nAs part of the 'Dinosaurs' topic, 1B will visit the Natural History Museum to see real fossils. The class will leave school at 9am and return around 14:30pm. Children should dress appropriately for the weather and bring a small rucksack. Packed lunches will be provided for those on school dinners; others should bring their own.
